          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Best library.one can study there.Read as much books as you want.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college had a very huge and big campus.",
          "name": "Harshpreet Kaur Pahuja",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Parking is good .Also,there are two parking for girls and one for working staff.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty way of teaching and help students in grooming as well",
          "name": "Srishti puri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure for the room is very good as 2 Ac is provided in every rooms.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Clean and spacious classrooms with smart board facility",
          "name": "Ishneet Kaur Matharoo",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Can opt for extra curricular activities as well",
